    <p>
      Content on this site reflects personal opinion and experience. Game rules, prices, product availability, and other factual details may change after publication. We make no warranty that any information is current, complete, or error-free.
    </p>

    <h2>Review copies and affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Where a product has been provided for review free of charge, this will be disclosed in the relevant post. This site may use affiliate links in future; any such links will be clearly marked. Affiliate relationships do not influence editorial opinions.
    </p>

    <h2>User conduct</h2>
    <p>
      You agree not to use this site or its contact form to submit unlawful, abusive, or spam content. We reserve the right to disregard or report any such submissions.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      This site is provided as-is, without warranty of any kind. Matt Gilbert is not liable for any damages arising from your use of or inability to use this site, or reliance on any content published here.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
    <p>
      These terms may be updated from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
    </p>
